Fluomics Daily Survey
===============================================

<% if @surveys.count == 1 %>
Please follow the link to complete your daily flu symptoms checklist.  It should only take a minute!
<% else %>
Today is the last day of tracking your flu symptoms!  Thank you so much for your participation.
<% end %>

<% @surveys.each do |survey| %>
